      "writtenOn": "2016-01-08T19:20:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "oh, no it can\u0027t, since calloc() could return NULL, and line 214 would blow up.\n\nIf size\u003d\u003d0, then perhaps we should assert that j-\u003esuppl_gid_count and j-\u003eflags.suppl_gids is set.\n\nPerhaps something like:\n\n  if (size \u003d\u003d 0) {\n    j-\u003esuppl_gid_count \u003d size;\n    j-\u003eflags.suppl_gids \u003d 1;\n    return 0;\n  }",
      "parentUuid": "4a74377b_15c2f47a",
      "range": {
