      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-01-08T19:20:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Well, if the list has size 0, we don\u0027t need to set the flag, which will then cause an empty call to setgroups later on minijail_enter(). Better not do anything? Do you think the semantics like this is weird?",
      "parentUuid": "4a74377b_15c2f47a",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 206,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 209,
        "endChar": 2
      },
      "revId": "84e67ddc37724b953c02c10f5a8154c3b226b0c0",
